@Kairoz For as long as I can remember, I was in a state of bliss, but then truths Such as the ones on this server made me realize.
What a horrible world this is. I wanted to change things, make things better, but then I realized "what's the point of going against the system" i gave up, and began being an actor I this theater because in my mind, I knew nothing could be done about it, oppression cannot exist without justice, justice cannot exist without oppression, corruption cannot exist without order.Nor order cannot exist without corruption, love cannot exist without hatred. Hatred cannot exist without love.
Light cannot exist without darkness.Nor  darkness cannot exist without light. If we were to abolish the system, another would replace it. And so would start the endless cycle of oppression and justice. The walls of peace I built upon the corpses of those who suffered violence and vice versa.

@everyone 

This is where we have organized and thoughtful discussions. Disagreements are allowed, just keep your ego in check. 

Follow the rules.
